66
00:05:49,780 --> 00:05:51,260
Your Highness remains calm in an emergency,

67
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:52,380
steady as Mount Tai.

68
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:54,140
Regarding today's ceremony,

69
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:55,660
though absent,

70
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:56,820
you've got

71
