83
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,520
Run!

84
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:37,740
Help!

85
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,240
Help!

86
00:07:41,580 --> 00:07:42,420
Save the Prince!

87
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:43,400
Help us!

88
00:07:48,590 --> 00:07:49,560
Help!

89
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:00,420
Toxic smoke!

90
00:08:31,060 --> 00:08:32,940
