92
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:42,180
Lu Chang.

93
00:09:06,100 --> 00:09:07,180
Don't come up!

94
00:09:08,060 --> 00:09:08,940
Lu Chang!

95
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:18,780
Lu Chang!

96
00:09:44,420 --> 00:09:45,300
Lu Chang.

97
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:52,740
Why are you here?

98
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:53,980
What's wrong with you?

99
00:09:54,260 --> 00:09:55,220
What happened?

100
