I've been poisoned.

101
00:09:56,020 --> 00:09:57,320
Something's wrong with the sky lanterns.

102
00:09:57,330 --> 00:09:57,970
Let's get out of here.

103
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:34,940
This way.

104
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:26,700
