- Let go of me!

108
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:31,740
Your Highness!

109
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:32,740
The flames are too fierce!

110
00:12:32,740 --> 00:12:34,380
- You cannot go in!
- I must help him!

111
00:12:34,660 --> 00:12:35,860
Let go!

112
00:12:36,180 --> 00:12:37,060
Shujun!

113
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:42,540
Shujun.

114
00:12:57,820 --> 00:12:58,940
You scared me to death.

115
00:13:00,660 --> 00:13:01,540
It's fine.

116
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,540
Everything is fine now.

117
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:09,300
What on earth is going on?

118
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:40,060
(To Prince Rui)

119
00:13:44,260 --> 00:13:45,700
Your Highness can withdraw first.

120
00:13:46,180 --> 00:13:47,900
There's a hidden door in the changing room.

121
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:49,660
But to get back inside will require

122
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:51,100
the time an incense stick burns.

123
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:52,860
You'll miss the Blessing Ceremony.

124
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:54,140
Lu Chang

125
00:13:55,260 --> 00:13:57,100
is going to take the risk in my stead?

126
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:09,060
Guards!

127
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:10,660
Guards!

128
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:16,140
The hidden door.

129
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:43,140
Lu Chang helped me.

130
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:49,420
Your Highness, the assassin is secured.

131
00:14:50,220 --> 00:14:51,660
He is Prince Yu's scheming pawn.

132
00:14:51,940 --> 00:14:52,900
Keep him alive as a testament.

133
00:14:53,260 --> 00:14:54,140
Yes!

134
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:55,580
Take him away!

135
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:56,980
Move!

136
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:01,300
Lu Chang is in danger now.

137
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:02,500
We must help him.

138
00:15:02,980 --> 00:15:03,860
Yes.

139
00:15:17,140 --> 00:15:18,020
Where is Su Tangli?

140
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:19,580
Guarded as ordered.

141
00:15:19,580 --> 00:15:20,540
She hasn't moved.

142
00:15:22,660 --> 00:15:24,260
Your Highness, bad news!

143
00:15:24,460 --> 00:15:25,700
Something happened

144
00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:26,740
at the Blessing Ceremony.

145
00:15:28,740 --> 00:15:29,820
How is that possible?

146
00:15:33,540 --> 00:15:35,540
(An)

147
00:15:50,180 --> 00:15:51,060
Lu Chang.

148
00:15:51,820 --> 00:15:52,740
Mingshu.

149
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:53,700
- Lady Mingshu.
- Lu Chang!

150
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:55,100
Lady Mingshu!

151
00:16:01,660 --> 00:16:06,060
(Liluo Pavilion)

152
00:16:06,380 --> 00:16:07,260
Lady Su,

153
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:08,740
where are you going at this hour?

154
00:16:09,460 --> 00:16:10,900
I need to see Prince Yu urgently.

155
00:16:11,020 --> 00:16:11,860
By His Highness's decree,

156
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:13,420
tonight, you're not allowed

157
00:16:13,420 --> 00:16:14,300
to leave the room.

158
00:16:14,460 --> 00:16:15,860
If his urgent matters are delayed,

159
00:16:15,860 --> 00:16:17,060
would you bear the consequences?

160
00:16:17,060 --> 00:16:18,340
Then I'll escort you.

161
00:16:31,780 --> 00:16:32,660
Thanks.

162
00:16:34,980 --> 00:16:35,940
Once this ends,

163
00:16:35,940 --> 00:16:37,540
find a way to leave.

164
00:16:37,540 --> 00:16:38,420
Lady Su,

165
00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:42,860
I'd like to follow you.

166
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:44,540
Unnecessary.

167
00:16:44,860 --> 00:16:46,100
You've done enough for me.

168
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:48,300
(Liluo Pavilion)
Prince Yu may be convicted.

169
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:50,100
While his attention lies elsewhere,

170
00:16:50,380 --> 00:16:51,420
seize the opportunity to flee.

171
00:16:58,460 --> 00:16:59,380
Lu Chang

172
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:00,980
ascended the altar in Prince Rui's stead.

173
00:17:00,980 --> 00:17:02,340
The sky lanterns ignited the altar.

174
00:17:02,580 --> 00:17:04,260
Lu Chang's fate remains unknown.

175
00:17:04,260 --> 00:17:05,180
But Prince Rui

176
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:06,900
slipped away from the locked changing room

177
00:17:07,060 --> 00:17:08,340
and captured our man.

178
00:17:08,620 --> 00:17:09,580
Their defenses

179
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:10,700
were meticulously staged!

180
00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:11,980
What?

181
00:17:13,140 --> 00:17:14,310
(Complete Impartiality)
Outrageous!

182
00:17:20,380 --> 00:17:22,060
By His Majesty's decree,

183
00:17:22,460 --> 00:17:24,140
Lu Zegang, Minister of Works,

184
00:17:24,210 --> 00:17:25,620
has failed in overseeing the construction

185
00:17:25,620 --> 00:17:26,700
of the Blessing Ceremony venue,

186
00:17:26,780 --> 00:17:28,020
disgracing His Majesty's benevolence

187
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:29,340
and dishonoring his ancestral legacy.

188
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,260
Hereby,

189
00:17:30,260 --> 00:17:31,860
he is stripped of rank and salary,

190
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:33,100
imprisoned immediately

191
00:17:33,260 --> 00:17:34,700
awaiting further judgment.

192
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:36,700
All members of his household

193
00:17:36,980 --> 00:17:38,540
are to be detained at their residence,

194
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:40,220
awaiting His Majesty's final decree.

195
00:17:40,420 --> 00:17:41,900
So decreed.

196
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:44,260
I

197
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:46,500
accept the decree

198
00:17:47,220 --> 00:17:48,220
with gratitude.

199
00:17:51,380 --> 00:17:52,560
My confidential documents are kept

200
00:17:52,570 --> 00:17:53,980
in the study's hidden compartment.

201
00:17:54,260 --> 00:17:55,340
Once I depart

202
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:56,620
and no one takes charge of the household,

203
00:17:56,740 --> 00:17:57,620
all responsibility

204
00:17:57,820 --> 00:17:59,420
falls to you.

205
00:18:00,220 --> 00:18:01,220
I understand, Father.

206
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:05,540
Take him away.

207
00:18:07,780 --> 00:18:08,700
No.

208
00:18:08,700 --> 00:18:09,580
Father.

209
00:18:09,740 --> 00:18:10,620
Master.

210
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:12,620
Master.

211
00:18:14,260 --> 00:18:15,140
No!

212
00:18:15,460 --> 00:18:16,340
Master!

213
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:43,580
(Grand Ambitions)

214
00:19:52,420 --> 00:19:54,100
Lu Zegang, you old fox.

215
00:19:54,740 --> 00:19:57,340
I knew you trusted me less than Feng did.

216
00:19:57,860 --> 00:19:59,620
How could you entrust

217
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:02,300
such secrets to me before being arrested?

218
00:20:03,180 --> 00:20:04,900
What malicious intentions!

219
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:07,020
Fortunately,

220
00:20:07,460 --> 00:20:09,100
I'm one step ahead.

221
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:12,340
Attempt to betray Prince Yu?

222
00:20:13,020 --> 00:20:14,140
Try again in your next life.

223
00:20:21,740 --> 00:20:22,820
Su Tangli?

224
00:20:37,780 --> 00:20:38,860
Su Tangli,

225
00:20:39,540 --> 00:20:40,420
why are you...

226
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:41,980
Why are you here?

227
00:20:50,020 --> 00:20:50,900
What?

228
00:20:51,220 --> 00:20:53,140
You think since Prince Yu doesn't trust me,

229
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:54,700
he'll have someone follow me all the way,

230
00:20:54,700 --> 00:20:56,420
so I won't be able to come here,

231
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:57,740
right?

232
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:03,740
You thought you were brilliant,

233
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:05,380
but your schemes

234
00:21:05,380 --> 00:21:07,060
were seen through long before.

235
00:21:07,460 --> 00:21:08,940
When you infiltrated the Lu Residence,

236
00:21:09,340 --> 00:21:10,260
I guessed

237
00:21:10,580 --> 00:21:11,940
you were going to unearth evidence

238
00:21:11,940 --> 00:21:13,660
against Prince Yu.

239
00:21:14,620 --> 00:21:16,140
How could I let you have your way?

240
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:17,180
You...

241
00:21:17,620 --> 00:21:18,460
You dare

242
00:21:18,460 --> 00:21:20,500
betray Prince Yu.

243
00:21:21,460 --> 00:21:23,180
I've never pledged loyalty to him.

244
00:21:23,180 --> 00:21:24,460
How am I supposed to betray him?

245
00:21:29,020 --> 00:21:30,540
Since you're so loyal,

246
00:21:31,220 --> 00:21:32,660
pave his path

247
00:21:32,660 --> 00:21:33,940
to the underworld.

248
00:21:41,540 --> 00:21:45,740
(Prince Yu's Jianglin Embezzlement)

249
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:48,940
(Ledger)

250
00:22:03,420 --> 00:22:04,300
Father,

251
00:22:06,380 --> 00:22:08,900
I can finally clear your name.

252
00:22:27,780 --> 00:22:28,660
Your Majesty,

253
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:30,780
this matter's roots spread too deep.

254
00:22:30,780 --> 00:22:32,340
I dare not make any decision.

255
00:22:32,340 --> 00:22:34,060
I require Your Majesty's instructions.

256
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:41,620
Are you implying

257
00:22:42,020 --> 00:22:43,620
that Lu Chang replaced Prince Rui

258
00:22:43,620 --> 00:22:44,740
at the altar, suspecting

259
00:22:45,290 --> 00:22:48,420
Prince Yu's orchestrated assassination?

260
00:22:49,580 --> 00:22:51,100
Also, Prince Yu

261
00:22:51,100 --> 00:22:52,660
is the mastermind

262
00:22:53,420 --> 00:22:54,820
of Su Changhua's case?

263
00:22:55,020 --> 00:22:56,460
I dare not make presumptions.

264
00:22:56,580 --> 00:22:57,980
I can only present the evidence

265
00:22:57,980 --> 00:22:59,780
I've gathered.

266
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:08,300
Issue my decree.

267
00:23:08,860 --> 00:23:10,940
Confine Prince Yu to his mansion

268
00:23:12,580 --> 00:23:13,900
awaiting thorough investigation

269
00:23:14,820 --> 00:23:16,100
by the Court of the Imperial Clan.

270
00:23:16,300 --> 00:23:17,180
Yes.

271
00:23:21,580 --> 00:23:23,900
(Liluo Pavilion)

272
00:23:24,180 --> 00:23:25,340
By His Majesty's decree,

273
00:23:30,380 --> 00:23:31,420
Prince Yu remains confined,

274
00:23:31,420 --> 00:23:32,900
cooperating with a thorough investigation.

275
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:34,020
No exit

276
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:35,060
without explicit edict.

277
00:23:35,460 --> 00:23:36,340
I

278
00:23:37,340 --> 00:23:38,220
obey the decree.

279
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:55,300
My silly consort.

280
00:23:59,660 --> 00:24:01,300
You hid everything from me.

281
00:24:02,540 --> 00:24:04,620
Do you truly see me as your consort?

282
00:24:09,020 --> 00:24:10,100
I was wrong.

283
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:15,620
I thought

284
00:24:17,460 --> 00:24:19,100
that if I told you the truth,

285
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:22,060
you'd be worried day and night.

286
00:24:24,460 --> 00:24:26,340
How could I let you suffer so?

287
00:24:27,780 --> 00:24:28,860
I didn't expect

288
00:24:31,460 --> 00:24:32,740
that you still went.

289
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:44,860
It was so dangerous,

290
00:24:46,020 --> 00:24:47,860
yet you tried to charge into the flames.

291
00:24:51,460 --> 00:24:52,700
Why are you so silly?

292
00:24:59,820 --> 00:25:01,900
Nothing mattered to me at that moment.

293
00:25:02,620 --> 00:25:04,820
I feared you'd abandon me.

294
00:25:05,410 --> 00:25:07,820
